After installing, import the CSS file from your global stylesheet (e.g. `src/styles.css`):

    @import "tailwindcss";
    @import "tw-animate-css";
    @import "shadcn/tailwind.css";
    @import "./styles/tokens.css";

Then load the three font families from Google Fonts in your index.html.
This file embodies the contract defined in section 3 of design-contract.md.
